Package csc1035.project2

Class Rooms

java.lang.Object
csc1035.project2.Rooms
@Entity(name="ROOMS")
public class Rooms
extends java.lang.Object
Entity class for Rooms. A room object contains: the room number (room_number) the type of the room (type) the maximum capacity of the room (max_capacity) the capacity under socially distant conditions (social_distancing_capacity)
